quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  21,11,Ebyalo bimeka bye twazikiriza ebyali byeyisa obubi olwo nno netuleeta abantu abalala (oluvanyuma lwa bwe)
  21,12,Bwe baamala okumanya nti ebibonerezo byaffe bijja olwo nnonebabidduka
  21,13,(Baagambibwa) nti temudduka era mudde eri ebyo bye mubadde mweyagaliramu era mudde mu mayumba gammwe luliba lumu mulibuuzibwa
  21,14,"Nebagamba nti: zitusanze mazima ffe twali tweyisa bubi"
  21,15,Okuwanjaga kwa bwe okwo kwali bwe kutyo okutuusa lwe twabafuula nga ennimiro ekunguddwa ne ggwawo
  21,16,Tetwatonda eggulu n'ensi n'ebiri wakati wa byombi nga bya muzannyo
  21,17,"Singa twayagala kweteerawo muzannyo, twaligukoze mu bano abali eno gye tuli singa twali ba kukikola"
  21,18,"Wabula tukasuka amazima ku bulimba negabuggyawo, olwo nno bwo nebuvaawo era mugenda kubonerezebwa olw'ebyo bye mwogera"
  21,19,"Bibye ebyo byonna ebiri mu ggulu ne mu nsi, n'abo abali waali tebeekuluntaza ku kumusinza era tebakaluubirirwa"
  21,20,Batendereza (Katonda) emisana n'ekiro tebakoowa
  21,21,Oba beeteerawo ba Katonda nga ba ku nsi nga bo be balizuukiza (abafu)
  21,22,"Singa (ensi n'eggulu) byalimu ba katonda abalala atali Katonda omu byombi byaliyonoonese, (ekyo nno kikulage) nti yasukkuluma Katonda Mukama omulabirizi wa Arishi kw'ebyo bye boogera"
  21,23,Tabuuzibwa ku byakola ate bo babuuzibwa
  21,24,"Abo bateekawo ba katonda ne baleka Katonda omu, gamba nti muleete obujulizi bwa mmwe (ku ekyo). Kuno kwe kubuulirira abali nange era kwe kubuulirira kw'abo abaakulembera wabula abasinga obungi mu bo (Abakaafiiri) tebamanyi mazima olwo nno bo bagakuba amabega"
  21,25,Era tetwatuma oluberyeberyelwo Mubaka yenna okugyako nga tumutumira obubaka nti tewali kisinzibwa kyonna (mu butuufu) okugyako nze (Katonda) kale munsinze
  21,26,"Era baagamba nti: Katonda ow'ekisa ekingi yeeteerawo omwana, musukkulumu (ku ebyo byonna) wabula (ba malayika bebamugattako) baddu abaweebwa ekitiibwa"
  21,27,Tebayinza kumukulembera na kigambo era bbo bakolera ku kiragirokye
  21,28,"Amanyi ebyo ebiri mu maaso gaabwe n'ebyo ebiri emabega waabwe, tebagenda kuwolereza okugyako oyo gwaliba asiimye nabo olw'okumutya beegendereza"
  21,29,"Oyo yenna mubo agamba nti mazima nze ndi Katonda naaleka Katonda omu, oyo tugenda kumusasula omuliro Jahannama. Bwe tutyo bwe tusasula abeeyisa obubi"